   ◊ı  Â¯˘¿

Option + e + any letter with a tick on it (vowels usually) -> é ó í
Option + ` + any letter with a backtick on it (vowels usually) -> è ò ì
Option + u + any letter with two dots on it (vowels usually) -> ë ö ï
Option + i + any letter with a roof on it (vowels usually) -> ê ô î
Option + n + any letter with a tilda on it (vowels usually) -> õ ã

You could also press and hold a letter to get variants
e -> èéêëēėę
o -> ôöòóœøōõ
